description:
Matthew J. Rainwater was originally from Louisiana and moved to Portland, Oregon.

He went to the Savannah College of Art & Design.

He works freelance as a cartoonist and illustrator, and self-publishes comics including Garage Raja and Trailer Park Warlock.
